(
"CompanyTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"RentTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"CompanyName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,

"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),

);
